-- Solaria Energia Reports a $35 Million Loss After Year-Earlier Profit
-- B y   S h a r o n   S m y t h
-- 2012-03-01T06:41:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-01/solaria-energia-reports-a-35-million-loss-after-year-earlier-profit.html
Solaria Energia y Medio Ambiente
SA (SLR)  posted a full-year loss of 26.34 million euros compared with
a profit of 6.5 million in the same period a year ago, the
company said in a filing to regulators late yesterday. Sales
fell to 121.55 million euros from 161.34  To contact the reporter on this story:
